    - Network connectivity issues
    - Server 500 errors
    - Database connection problems
    end note
    
    PS -> FE: 46b. Rollback optimistic updates
    PS -> FE: 47b. Show error notification
    FE -> U: 48b. Display "Try again" message
    note right
    **Error Recovery:**
    - Restore previous state
    - Show user-friendly message
    - Provide retry option
    - Log error for debugging
    end note
end

